  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mindbytes: Learn to read Japanese is the most fun way to learn the Japanese writing systems of Katakana and Hiragana.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249020/extras/2ef83d3d7ab7436f15fd57772e45fdb1.avif?t=1674418581\" width=630 height=131 /></span><br><br>• Learn each character of both Katakana and Hiragana including its name and pronunciation<br>• Click the characters to learn how they are pronounced<br>• Think fast and challenge yourself to reach the highest score in the fast-paced and fun game mode<br>• Clicking the correct character earns you time, but getting the wrong answer causes a time penalty<br>• Get as many correct answers as possible before time runs out<br>• Reference flash-cards to look up any characters you haven't memorised yet<br>• Improve your language skills while learning two new writing systems<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249020/extras/5c054d0bf719b9b7a8f33c37d967ae1b.avif?t=1674418581\" width=630 height=131 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Mindbytes: Learn to read Japanese is the most fun way to learn the Japanese writing systems of Katakana and Hiragana.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249020/extras/2ef83d3d7ab7436f15fd57772e45fdb1.avif?t=1674418581\" width=630 height=131 /></span><br><br>• Learn each character of both Katakana and Hiragana including its name and pronunciation<br>• Click the characters to learn how they are pronounced<br>• Think fast and challenge yourself to reach the highest score in the fast-paced and fun game mode<br>• Clicking the correct character earns you time, but getting the wrong answer causes a time penalty<br>• Get as many correct answers as possible before time runs out<br>• Reference flash-cards to look up any characters you haven't memorised yet<br>• Improve your language skills while learning two new writing systems<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249020/extras/5c054d0bf719b9b7a8f33c37d967ae1b.avif?t=1674418581\" width=630 height=131 /></span>",
